#### PR description:

The goal of this PR is a heavy refactoring of the package `CondTools/SiStrip`, as a follow-up of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/35999.
   * plugin files have now class declarations within the implementation `.cc` file (headers are removed);
   * a bug in the `SiStripDetInfoFileReader` usage, introduced at https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/34285, is corrected.
   * removed `SealModules.cc` file;
   * generalized modernization of the code where possible;
   * introduced test units;

#### PR validation:

Validation relies on the (augmented) unit tests, which run successfully.

